>  173: We release \textbf{mAceReason-Math}, a multilingual version of a filtered subset of AceReason-Math, covering 14 languages in total and comprising 10k+ translated problems across 13 languages, cleaned versions of the original English problems, a fully parallel train split of 7{,}620 samples per language, and a human-validated test set of 190 samples. Our pipeline combines targeted cleaning with iterative LLM translation and native-speaker checks to produce faithful, high-quality problems.

